,"msg":"一班畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9f7a3870374e518813bf41dc1a49272885129d","tid":1880003,"uid":107681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6cab7df684f3712d504c6a9ec27d3fca4bb5e6a9","tid":1880003,"uid":256143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"以前d狗好怕區議員，其實區議員可以有乜權力令狗咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"一來以前係奶共派班垃圾，同政府圍威喂<br />\n<br />\n二來e半年狗隊權力已經高過曬成個政府<br />\n<br />\n區區一個pc仔都可以屌鳩張建忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b040bcacd41e3c999ac78c3bb71679169ac01c","tid":1880003,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e9f7a3870374e518813bf41dc1a49272885129d","tid":1880003,"uid":107681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6cab7df684f3712d504c6a9ec27d3fca4bb5e6a9","tid":1880003,"uid":256143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"以前d狗好怕區議員，其實區議員可以有乜權力令狗咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"一來以前係奶共派班垃圾，同政府圍威喂<br />\n<br />\n二來e半年狗隊權力已經高過曬成個政府<br />\n<br />\n區區一個pc仔都可以屌鳩張建忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"珍"},{"pid":"4937e7280968474e51d84f96bfc83009a6837a49","tid":1880003,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b51728ed7b2696d6e7947cf6fdc255750d20542","tid":1880003,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7e69e4315dc010212fedc59ec46334f8a5152a","tid":1880003,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"